subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened capacities of national human rights institutions
subproject.description: This initiation plan will devise and implement short-term measures aimed at enhancing access to justice and expediting processes within the judicial system.  The key outputs for the project are:  a) Justice dispensed in the 2580 backlog of cases at the court; b) High Court Rules amended; c) Rules of Procedures for the Courts System drafted and adopted; d) Capacities of the Judicial and Administrative Officers strengthened in leadership and management; e) Operational Manuals for the Judiciary and Courts System developed; f) Website for the Judiciary developed; g) Magistrates courts equipped with state of the art computers.
subproject.title: SUPPORT TO THE JUDICIARY OF TH
